Metadata.Title: King's Order: ALPHAs
Metadata.Description: You are assigned to kill the alphas of the Los Santos Police Department from Familia Green. Each of the alphas have disguised themselves with fake names as they attend their secret ceremony that commences annually.A-1  Godfrey SkidmoreA-2 Roman DancerA-3 Dakota ZolaA-4 Camilla CraigA-5 Kenneth O'Dell
